      "content": "i know... i've tried everything. i talk to people, i try to stay busy, but it just feels like i'm performing. it's exhausting pretending that life is actually worth the effort when nothing feels real anymore. it’s like i’m just stuck in this loop of sadness and there's no way out of it. it just feels so permanent.",
